SELECT movie_companies.company_type_id, company_type.kind FROM company_type, movie_companies WHERE movie_companies.note < '(1979) (USA: Midwest) (theatrical) (dubbed)' AND movie_companies.company_id <= 15426 AND movie_companies.movie_id < 2015887 AND movie_companies.company_type_id >= 2 AND company_type.kind <= 'miscellaneous companies' AND company_type.id <= 1 AND movie_companies.id >= 1321970 ORDER BY movie_companies.company_type_id DESC, company_type.kind ASC

SELECT aka_title.production_year, title.md5sum, kind_type.kind FROM title JOIN aka_title ON aka_title.movie_id = title.id JOIN kind_type ON kind_type.id = aka_title.kind_id WHERE title.id >= 386873 AND title.imdb_index <= 'I' AND title.title <= '(#1.5035)' AND kind_type.kind <> 'episode' ORDER BY title.md5sum ASC

SELECT cast_info.person_role_id, name.name_pcode_nf, role_type.role FROM role_type JOIN cast_info ON cast_info.role_id = role_type.id JOIN name ON name.id = cast_info.person_id WHERE name.surname_pcode < 'G625' AND name.gender < 'f' AND cast_info.person_role_id <= 54876 AND name.md5sum > 'bcbdbc02675d847657d524154326f07a' AND name.imdb_index < 'III'

SELECT person_info.person_id, name.name_pcode_nf, aka_name.name_pcode_nf FROM person_info JOIN name ON name.id = person_info.person_id JOIN aka_name ON aka_name.person_id = name.id WHERE person_info.id >= 372300 AND name.id <= 202842 AND aka_name.name_pcode_cf > 'M4521' AND aka_name.md5sum <> '7cf23d5fa36a011c05997cbe37cfaf14' ORDER BY name.name_pcode_nf DESC, aka_name.name_pcode_nf ASC

SELECT movie_link.linked_movie_id, movie_keyword.id, title.series_years FROM movie_keyword JOIN title ON title.id = movie_keyword.movie_id JOIN movie_link ON movie_link.movie_id = title.id WHERE title.production_year >= 1902 AND title.id <= 724807 AND title.episode_of_id <= 509834 AND title.md5sum <= '94a7ef96e356bf404df375d3d184a246'

SELECT title.imdb_index, aka_title.movie_id, comp_cast_type.id, kind_type.id, complete_cast.id FROM kind_type JOIN aka_title ON aka_title.kind_id = kind_type.id JOIN title ON title.id = aka_title.movie_id JOIN complete_cast ON complete_cast.movie_id = title.id JOIN comp_cast_type ON comp_cast_type.id = complete_cast.status_id WHERE aka_title.kind_id <> 7 AND title.episode_nr >= 237 AND comp_cast_type.id >= 2

SELECT title.episode_nr, movie_info.id, movie_link.linked_movie_id FROM movie_link JOIN title ON title.id = movie_link.movie_id JOIN movie_info ON movie_info.movie_id = title.id WHERE title.md5sum <= 'ba830df41cf756fd345e2b9683690c19' AND title.kind_id >= 2 AND title.title >= 'Rahma' AND title.phonetic_code < 'I243' AND movie_info.info_type_id <> 43

SELECT title.id, movie_info.movie_id, complete_cast.status_id FROM movie_info JOIN title ON title.id = movie_info.movie_id JOIN complete_cast ON complete_cast.movie_id = title.id WHERE title.kind_id < 7 AND title.series_years < '1996-????' AND movie_info.note >= 'darkknight575' AND title.md5sum >= '888ce491c23a67e2c0dfd2899776a39f' ORDER BY title.id ASC, complete_cast.status_id ASC

SELECT movie_info.info, info_type.id FROM movie_info, info_type WHERE info_type.info < 'agent address' AND movie_info.movie_id >= 2129205 AND movie_info.info >= '$6,886,080 (USA) (9 November 2003)' AND info_type.id > 62 ORDER BY movie_info.info ASC, info_type.id ASC
